title: Double-Six Dominoes 2
description:
ABOUT THIS GAME:

Double-Six Dominoes follows the rules known as \&#039;Muggins\&#039; or \&#039;The
Five Game\&#039;. Play against the computer or another human player
via the Internet. This program is very easy to use and will
actually teach you to play dominoes. Then, when you are ready,
switch to Advanced mode for a more challenging game. The playing
field can now be maximized, the rules can be modified for single
or multiple spinner games, rounds start with your choice of
dominoe (instead of largest double), and the starting hand size
and draw rules are customizable.

Version 2 increases strength of computer opponent, feattures
options for modifying game rules.
